BusinessTech partnered with Wyzetalk to launch the South African Employee Survey to gain insight into workplace happiness and productivity. Wyzetalk focuses on facilitating meaningful connections through targeted information and content that leads to improved productivity for clients. The South African Employee Survey consists of 8 simple questions, which gives employees the opportunity to rate their workplace communication and operational efficiency. The survey will take less than 1 minute to complete, and people who take part in the survey can win prizes worth R4,000. Complete the survey here: South African Employee Survey This article was published in partnership with Wyzetalk.